data.description: Pompeii style custom home in historic district of Gaffney. This architecturally designed home is centrally located near shopping, schools, medical facilities, library, park and Limestone College. This home has lots of space, high ceilings, large rooms, stone fireplace, imported Portugal(hand painted) tiles, marvelous hardwoods (tidewater cypress, oak, walnut), crown moldings, wet bar, coy pond, hand carved mantle, it\'s own greenhouse, water features and a multitude of storage(even areas to expand finished square footage if desired) and it\'s own Log Cabin. This is a must see! Don\'t let this one get away; learn more about the history of this home, make an appointment to view today.
